org.mitre.provenance.plusobject

Class PLUSActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.provenance.surrogate.Surrogateable
      • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.PLUSObject
        • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.PLUSActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<Object>, SourcedObject, PropertyCapable

    public class PLUSActivity
extends PLUSObject
    An abstract activity description. Note that this is *not* an instance of the activity's execution. For that, you want PLUSInvocation.
    Author:
    DMALLEN
